1 Exhibit 8.1 行は年齢群、列は健康カテゴリ

.health0 <- read_excel("health.xls")
## New names:
## * `` -> ...1
names(.health0)
## [1] "...1" "VG"   "G"    "R"    "B"    "VB"
.health0 %>% rename(Age_G = ...1) %>% mutate(Age_G = as.factor(Age_G)) -> .health
.health %>% gather(key=cond,val=n,-Age_G) %>% xtabs(n ~ Age_G + cond,.) -> .health.tbl0
.health.tbl0[,c(5,2,3,1,4)] -> .health.tbl

2.1 ca::ca でやってみる

  • ca::ca のxx$colcoord は標準座標
lb <- c("VeryGood","Good","regular","Bad","VeryBad")
res.ca$colcoord[,1] %>% as_tibble() %>% ggplot(aes(x = value, y = 0)) + geom_point() -> p
p <- p + geom_hline(yintercept = 0,lty="dashed")
p <- p + geom_text_repel(label=lb,size=3)
#p <- p + scale_x_continuous(breaks=c(-0.4,-0.2,0,0.2,0.4,0.6,0.8))
p

2.2 Exhibit 8.2 FactoMineR::CA でやってみる()　

  • FactoMiner::CA のxx$coord は主座標（ca::caは標準座標）
#lb <- rownames(res.CA$col$coord)
lb <- c("VeryGood","Good","regular","Bad","VeryBad")
res.CA$col$coord[,1] %>% as_tibble() %>% ggplot(aes(x = value, y = 0)) + geom_point() -> p
p <- p + geom_hline(yintercept = 0,lty="dashed")
p <- p + geom_text_repel(label=lb,size=3)
p <- p + scale_x_continuous(breaks=c(-0.4,-0.2,0,0.2,0.4,0.6,0.8))
p

3 Exhibit 8.3

  • col coord を主座標、row coord を標準座標で重ねる
lb <- c("VeryGood","Good","regular","Bad","VeryBad")
lc <- rownames(res.CA$row$coord)

#res.CA %>% str()
res.CA$eig[1,1] -> inertia

bind_rows(res.CA$col$coord[,1] %>% as.tibble()  %>% mutate(dim="colum", lab = lb),
          tibble(value= res.CA$row$coord[,1] * 1/inertia) %>% mutate(dim="row",lab = lc)) -> col_and_row
## Warning: `as.tibble()` is deprecated as of tibble 2.0.0.
## Please use `as_tibble()` instead.
## The signature and semantics have changed, see `?as_tibble`.
## This warning is displayed once every 8 hours.
## Call `lifecycle::last_warnings()` to see where this warning was generated.
col_and_row %>% ggplot(aes(x = value, y = 0)) + geom_point() -> p
p <- p + geom_hline(yintercept = 0,lty="dashed")
p <- p + geom_text_repel(label= col_and_row$lab, size=3)
#p <- p + scale_x_continuous(breaks=c(-0.4,-0.2,0,0.2,0.4,0.6,0.8))
p

4.1 固有値の平方根をスケーリングファクタとしてprinとstdが結び付けられている。

  • ca が表示するDim.1　VB = 2.076021（これSTD？）、CAは、VB = 0.767（これprin？）。この間は、主慣性（固有値）のルートになっている。
  • prin = std * sqrt(λ) でいいか。
2.076021 * sqrt(0.136603)
## [1] 0.7672941
  • Exhibit 8.4 の左(Profile coordinate)は、0.767、右のVertex coordinate は、1.004 になっている。

5 Exhibit 8.5

.health.tbl
##        cond
## Age_G    VG   G   R   B  VB
##   16-24 243 789 167  18   6
##   25-34 220 809 164  35   6
##   35-44 147 658 181  41   8
##   45-54  90 469 236  50  16
##   55-64  53 414 306 106  30
##   65-74  44 267 284  98  20
##   75+    20 136 157  66  17
.health %>% gather(key=cond,val=n,-Age_G) -> .health.long
res.CA$col$coord[,1] -> x #主座標 Health cond named vector になっている。recodeで使う
res.ca$rowcoord[,1] -> y  #標準座標 Age_G
.health.long %>% mutate(xval = recode(cond,!!!x),yval = recode(Age_G,!!!y)) -> .health4ballon

# ref: p90 of Keon-Woong Moon,2016,"Learn ggplot2 Using Shiny App",Springer
ggplot(.health4ballon,aes(x=-xval,y=-yval,size=n)) + scale_size_area(max_size = 15) +
  geom_point(fill='cornsilk',shape=22) -> p
p <- p + xlab("HEALTH CATEGORY") + ylab("AGE GROUP") + ggtitle("Exhibit 8.5")
p <- p + scale_x_continuous(breaks = -x,labels = names(x))
p
